MOONLIGHT FORCE FOCUS

   Using this spell, the lunar mage can call on the ultimate
   power of the Blood Moon, to devastating effect.  He can
   unleash the energy as an explosive burst of crushing
   force on the general vicinity with the command 'mfocus',
   or he can use the force to crush two chosen targets together
   with the power of gravity, using 'mfocus <target> and
   <target2>'.  This second use is more deadly due to the
   greater concentration of force, and also takes less time
   to recover from, due to the narrower range of effect.

 GL: 15  COST: 200
